original_title: Pretty Guardian Sailor Moon Classic Concert 2018
overview: Video of Pretty Guardian Sailor Moon Classic Concert 2018, which was held on August 28 & 29, 2018 in Tokyo and September 7, 2018 in Osaka. Conductor: Yuri Niita, Guests: Mitsuko Horie, Akiko Kosaka, Mariko Terashita, and Suguru (from TSUKEMEN).
title: Pretty Guardian Sailor Moon Classic Concert 2018
